<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁开始往家的方向走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，他走出了沙漠，回到了那个凉爽的、绿色的花园里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到了他和马格里布休息过的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个人！”他说，“我再也不想看到他了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35482</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁看到城门的时候，他走得更快了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很快就穿过了集市，走向有很多房子的弯曲的街道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向自己的房子跑去，推开了门，然后走了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁的妈妈放下了纱布，举起双手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“感谢上帝！”她大声说，“你还活着！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈！”阿拉丁叫了一声就昏了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的儿子！”泽巴拿着一杯水走向她刚刚昏倒的儿子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她温柔地把水倒在阿拉丁的头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”他大叫着醒来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我担心得都生病了。”泽巴说，“你这一天一夜都去哪里了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会告诉你的。”阿拉丁一边擦干水一边说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我被带到了离家很远的地方。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我被送到地底下，然后被关了起来，被抛下等死。我又饿又冷。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“而我现在好像要被水淹死了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>泽巴的双眼睁得很大，杯子掉在了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“到底发生了什么？你的伯父在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他不是我伯父。”阿拉丁大声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是个骗子，是个邪恶的魔法师。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141878</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我都不敢相信我居然还活着！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141879</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是你伯父说……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他不是我伯父！他的善良都是假的！他的承诺都是诡计。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他一路上都在计划要杀了我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>泽巴的脸变得苍白，阿拉丁抱住了她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163700</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把一路上发生的事情都告诉了她，包括宝库和灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他给她看了玻璃水果和灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就是因为这些玻璃水果。”他解释说，“我不能把灯拿给马格里布。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他太生气了，就把我活埋在宝库里走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁深深地坐在垫子上，说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我从昨天到现在只吃了一块饼干和一个无花果。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拿着这个，阿拉丁。”他妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她给了儿子家里最后一片面包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他吃完了之后，就在吃饭的地方睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223145</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁到第二天中午才醒过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223146</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他坐起来把手放在头后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我饿了，妈妈。”他说，“有东西吃吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237549</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>泽巴边纺羊毛边摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“家里已经没有多余的食物了，我的孩子，也没有钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我纺了一些纱。我把它们拿到集市上去卖掉。然后我就可以买一些面包。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别再纺布了。”阿拉丁从垫子上站起来说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会把这个铜灯拿到集市去卖掉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把灯放进后面的口袋里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等一下，儿子。”泽巴说，“那个灯很脏。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果我把它擦亮，应该可以卖个更好的价钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284022</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿了一块抹布擦那盏灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这个时候，一团烟雾在头顶盘旋，房间里面响起了音乐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生什么事情了？”泽巴大声说，“救命啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你有什么愿望就命令我吧。”烟雾中出现了一个声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>音乐停了，烟雾也散去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>又一个精灵站在了他们面前！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>